snippet.title: Armored Warfare - Open Beta Trailer
snippet.description:
Obsidian Entertainment & My.com are proud to present the start of Armored Warfare Open Beta phase. Play Armored Warfare for free: http://go.aw.my.com/ArmoredWarfareYT  

The Open Beta begins October 8th!
Get a Head-Start on October 1st by buying one of our Founder's Packs here: http://aw.my.com/us/founders-packs !

Armored Warfare is a free-to-play massively multiplayer online tactical military video game that puts you in control of modern tanks, armored vehicles and more. 

Our Social Links
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/OfficialArmoredWarfare
Twitter: https://twitter.com/ArmoredWar
Instagram: COMING SOON
Twitch: http://www.twitch.tv/officialarmoredwarfare
Play Armored Warfare for free: http://go.aw.my.com/ArmoredWarfareYT  

What is Armored Warfare?
Obsidian Entertainment & My.com are proud to present Armored Warfare. Armored Warfare is a free-to-play massively multiplayer online tactical military video game that puts you in control of modern tanks, armored vehicles and more! Armored Warfare features stunning next-gen visuals, dynamic destructible environments, customizable vehicles and intense team-based gameplay where players work to crush each other with the power of modern combat vehicles in a free-to-compete experience
